Desc.CHS: 染血骑士持有的黯淡金属杯皿。外壁因为烟熏与凝结的血变得漆黑如夜。
Desc.EN: The dark metallic vessel owned by the Bloodstained Knight. Its exterior has been stained as black as the night by smoke and coagulated blood.

Desc.CHS: 黏在骑士斗篷上的鸦羽。因为反复沾染大量的黑血已经被彻底染成墨色。
Desc.EN: A raven feather pinned to a knight's cape. Countless bloodstains have dyed it pitch black.

Desc.CHS: 骑士用来遮掩自己面目的铁面具，关于面具下的容貌几何曾有无数猜想。
Desc.EN: The iron mask the knight used to conceal their identity. Many have speculated about the face behind the mask.

Desc.CHS: 被血染黑，变得如钢铁一般坚硬的干花。对故主而言，是某种纪念品吧。
Desc.EN: A dried flower stained black with blood and now as hard as steel. Probably some sort of a memento for its former master.

Desc.CHS: 骑士曾经使用过的时计。其中的液体已经完全凝结了，失去了计时功能。
Desc.EN: A timepiece once used by a knight. The liquid inside has dried up, rendering it useless.

Desc.CHS: 曾经属于旧日蒙德贵族的首饰瓮，空空如也的腹内仿佛回响着哀戚的风声。
Desc.EN: An ornamental urn that once belonged to the old aristocrats of Mondstadt. Mournful winds seem to echo within its empty interior.

Desc.CHS: 旧日蒙德贵族会猎时在帽檐上佩戴的羽饰。如今傲然挺立依旧，不谙时光。
Desc.EN: A feathered hat accessory worn by the old aristocrats of Mondstadt on hunts. It still stands proudly as if no time has passed.

Desc.CHS: 曾经属于旧日蒙德贵族的舞会面具，那空洞的眼眶依旧凝望着昔日的盛景。
Desc.EN: A masquerade mask worn by the old aristocrats of Mondstadt. Its hollow eyes are fixated on the golden days of the past.

Desc.CHS: 绸缎制成的璃色花，常在典雅场合佩戴。如今仍像被抛弃的那天一样鲜明。
Desc.EN: A satin flower with a glossy finish, fit for an elegant gathering. It still looks as distinguished as it did on the day it was cast aside.

Desc.CHS: 曾经属于旧日蒙德贵族的怀表，随漫长的谱系流传至今，见证了过往年岁。
Desc.EN: A pocket watch that once belonged to the old aristocrats of Mondstadt. Passed down from generation to generation, it has witnessed many years of history.

Desc.CHS: 曾经梦想烧尽世间魔物的炎之魔女留下的流火之甕。瓶中火永不熄灭，一如其人。
Desc.EN: A flame-spitting urn left behind by the Crimson Witch of Flames, who once dreamt of burning away all the demons in the world. The fire in the urn burns eternally, as did its former master.

Desc.CHS: 曾经梦想烧尽世间魔物的魔女触碰过的鸟羽，在恒常的燃烧中挥发着烈焰的温度。
Desc.EN: A bird feather touched by the witch who once dreamt of burning away all the demons in the world. Its eternal flame burns hot.

Desc.CHS: 曾经梦想烧尽世间魔物的炎之魔女曾经戴过的帽子。宽大的帽檐能遮挡她的视线。
Desc.EN: A hat once worn by the witch who dreamt of burning away all of the demons in the world. The large brim blocked her sight.

Desc.CHS: 曾经梦想烧尽世间魔物的魔女触碰过的花朵。无名的火舌温暖地舔舐触碰它的人。
Desc.EN: A flower touched by the witch who once dreamt of burning away all the demons in the world. The anonymous flames affectionately caress the hands of those who touch it.

Desc.CHS: 曾经梦想烧尽世间魔物的魔女佩戴的时计。其中流淌着的是魔女献给火焰的岁月。
Desc.EN: A timepiece worn by the witch who dreamt of burning away all the demons in the world. The years the witch dedicated to the flames flow within.

Desc.CHS: 曾经梦想烧尽世间魔物的炎之魔女留下的流火之甕。瓶中火永不熄灭，一如其人。
Desc.EN: A flame-spitting urn left behind by the Crimson Witch of Flames, who once dreamt of burning away all the demons in the world. The fire in the urn burns eternally, as did its former master.

Desc.EN: A timepiece worn by the witch who dreamt of burning away all the demons in the world. The years the witch dedicated to the flames flow within.

Desc.CHS: 注入无辜者鲜血的祝圣的仪式之杯，祈愿雷鸣回荡其中。最终溢满了如雷的盛怒。
Desc.EN: A ceremonial cup that holds the blood of the innocent. It is brimming with the thundering fury of the prayers that echo within.

Desc.CHS: 带电的雷之羽，是雷之魔鸟降下残酷的报应。遗落的羽毛仍闪烁着它盛怒的雷光。
Desc.EN: A lightning-charged feather that still flickers with the wrath of the Thunderbird's cruel retribution.

Desc.CHS: 古代崇拜雷之魔鸟的萨满曾戴过的头冠，虔诚的信仰却无法打动喜怒无常的魔兽。
Desc.EN: A crown once worn by an ancient shaman who worshiped the Thunderbird. The capricious beast remained unmoved by the shaman's devotion.

Desc.CHS: 在劫难之日侥幸免受纷乱的践踏与紫之火的忿恨之摧，于惨象中幸存的雷色之花。
Desc.EN: A lightning-infused flower, somehow spared the fate of being trodden underfoot or reduced to ash by the furious purple fire, making it the sole survivor on the day of disaster.

Desc.CHS: 信奉雷鸟的部族预告天空的雷之主降临的沙漏。因一族的末路陷入了永远的静止。
Desc.EN: The hourglass used to foretell the coming of the Thunderbird by the tribe that worshiped it. It has fallen into eternal silence now that the tribe is no more.

Desc.CHS: 注入无辜者鲜血的祝圣的仪式之杯，祈愿雷鸣回荡其中。最终溢满了如雷的盛怒。

Desc.EN: A crown once worn by an ancient shaman who worshiped the Thunderbird. The capricious beast remained unmoved by the shaman's devotion.

Desc.EN: The hourglass used to foretell the coming of the Thunderbird by the tribe that worshiped it. It has fallen into eternal silence now that the tribe is no more.

Desc.CHS: 与北风同行的骑士留下的空之杯，凛冬的霜之息依旧盈满其中。
Desc.EN: A goblet of eonothem left behind by the knight who walked with the North Wind. The chill of the bitter winter frost still lingers within.

Desc.CHS: 与北风同行的骑士于雪中拾获的鸟羽，如今依旧静候解冻之刻。
Desc.EN: A bird feather that was picked up by the knight who walked with the North Wind in the snow. It still awaits the day when it will thaw.

Desc.CHS: 与北风同行的骑士所戴的冠冕，以凛冬的寒冰与白银打造而成。
Desc.EN: The crown worn by the knight who walked with the North Wind. It was forged using winter ice and silver.

Desc.CHS: 陷入静默的冰之花，凝固在摘下的一刻，是骑士不离身的纪念。
Desc.EN: A flower that has been frozen in time from the moment it was picked. The knight kept it as a memento forever after.

Desc.CHS: 与北风同行的骑士曾用的时计，内部是永不消去的雪砂与霜风。
Desc.EN: A timepiece once used by the knight who walked with the North Wind. A never-ending snowstorm rages within.

Desc.EN: A goblet of eonothem left behind by the knight who walked with the North Wind. The chill of the bitter winter frost still lingers within.

Desc.EN: A timepiece once used by the knight who walked with the North Wind. A never-ending snowstorm rages within.

Desc.CHS: 外形奇妙的古代水壶，内侧安装着琴弦，随流水而奏出无旋律的奇妙乐声。
Desc.EN: An ancient, strangely-shaped canteen. The interior is fitted with harp strings, which play a wondrous tune as the water flows out.

Desc.CHS: 青蓝色的箭羽，并未在漫长岁月中褪色破碎。似乎带来了落珠流水的琴声。
Desc.EN: An azure arrow fletching that has neither faded nor splintered with the passage of time. The sound of running water seems to linger around it.

Desc.CHS: 尽管饱经风霜，但依旧光彩照人的礼帽。其中似乎回荡着古老悠扬的乐声。
Desc.EN: A top hat that has managed to retain its radiance despite braving the elements for time untold. An ancient tune still resonates within.

Desc.CHS: 小小的花形徽章。侧耳细听的话，仿佛能听到悠扬的笛声和清新的歌唱声。
Desc.EN: A small flower-shaped insignia. If you listen carefully, you can almost hear a flute playing and voices singing.

Desc.CHS: 为乐团的演奏计时的沙漏，曾发出利落的声响。如今他们的表演已经落幕。
Desc.EN: An hourglass used to keep time during a band performance. It once made a crisp sound, but their performance has since ended.

Desc.CHS: 外形奇妙的古代水壶，内侧安装着琴弦，随流水而奏出无旋律的奇妙乐声。
Desc.EN: An ancient, strangely-shaped canteen. The interior is fitted with harp strings, which play a wondrous tune as the water flows out.

Desc.CHS: 为乐团的演奏计时的沙漏，曾发出利落的声响。如今他们的表演已经落幕。
Desc.EN: An hourglass used to keep time during a band performance. It once made a crisp sound, but their performance has since ended.

Desc.CHS: 绿野猎人曾用过的水囊，里面的空间远比想象的更大。
Desc.EN: A water pouch used by the Viridescent Venerer. Its capacity is much greater than one would expect.

Desc.CHS: 曾经一瞬贯穿猎物的箭矢的尾羽。如今依旧平整光洁。
Desc.EN: The fletching of an arrow that once pierced right through its prey, but somehow still remains spotless.

Desc.CHS: 曾属于绿野猎人的骄傲头冠，如同原野之风一般青翠。
Desc.EN: A proud crown that once belonged to the Viridescent Venerer. It is as lush and green as the breezes of the wild.

Desc.CHS: 曾经遍布某地的野花。离开了大地，被猎人佩在胸前。
Desc.EN: A wild flower that was once a ubiquitous sight in its homeland. It was picked by a hunter who wore it on their chest.

Desc.CHS: 猎人曾经随身携带的奇妙仪器，永远指向自己的猎物。
Desc.EN: A wondrous instrument that a hunter once wore. It forever points towards their prey.

Desc.CHS: 绿野猎人曾用过的水囊，里面的空间远比想象的更大。
Desc.EN: A water pouch used by the Viridescent Venerer. Its capacity is much greater than one would expect.

Desc.EN: The fletching of an arrow that once pierced right through its prey, but somehow still remains spotless.

Desc.EN: A proud crown that once belonged to the Viridescent Venerer. It is as lush and green as the breezes of the wild.

Desc.CHS: 曾经遍布某地的野花。离开了大地，被猎人佩在胸前。
Desc.EN: A wild flower that was once a ubiquitous sight in its homeland. It was picked by a hunter who wore it on their chest.

Desc.CHS: 猎人曾经随身携带的奇妙仪器，永远指向自己的猎物。
Desc.EN: A wondrous instrument that a hunter once wore. It forever points towards their prey.

Desc.CHS: 古代的角斗士痛饮胜利之酒的金杯。直到他倒下的那一刻，酒杯被他自己的岁月灌满。
Desc.EN: The golden cup a champion gladiator drank from in ancient times. It brimmed with his glory for years until the fateful day of his fall.

Desc.CHS: 如隼般自在的梦想之羽。在传奇生涯的终点，无羁的飞鸟在他的心口覆上了这根羽毛。
Desc.EN: A feather of dreams that soars free like an eagle. At the end of the gladiator's legendary life, this parting gift was left upon his chest by a bird that knew true freedom.

Desc.CHS: 古代传奇角斗士的头盔，曾沾染了无数敌手的鲜血，也曾骄傲地接受无数观众的欢呼。
Desc.EN: The helmet of a legendary gladiator from ancient times, who would proudly stretch out his bloodied arms to welcome the thunderous applause of his audience.

Desc.CHS: 无人知晓传奇的斗士为何始终将这朵小花戴在胸口，这是残酷的战士身上唯一的弱点。
Desc.EN: No one knows why the legendary gladiator wore this flower on his chest. It was the brutal warrior's only weakness.

Desc.CHS: 记录了角斗士血染剧场的年月的时计。之于其人，则象征着去往终获自由之日的道路。
Desc.EN: A timepiece that recorded the gladiator's days in the bloodstained Colosseum. To him, it counted down the days on his long road to freedom.

Desc.CHS: 古代的角斗士痛饮胜利之酒的金杯。直到他倒下的那一刻，酒杯被他自己的岁月灌满。

Desc.EN: A timepiece that recorded the gladiator's days in the bloodstained Colosseum. To him, it counted down the days on his long road to freedom.

Desc.CHS: 属于红茶而不属于烈酒，属于芳甜而不属于苦涩的杯皿。
Desc.EN: A vessel made with sweet black tea in mind rather than bitter liquor.

Desc.CHS: 寄托谁人的思念的羽饰，就如与风一同去往远方的候鸟。
Desc.EN: A feathered accessory that carries the longing for a certain someone, like a migratory bird on the wind.

Desc.CHS: 精心保养的女士帽，即使是眼角的皱纹也可以完美遮盖。
Desc.EN: A meticulously well-maintained woman's hat that keeps wrinkles safely out of sight.

Desc.CHS: 永远娇嫩的鲜花，历经长久时光仍不枯萎地散发着芬芳。
Desc.EN: A fragrant flower that will bloom for all eternity and never wither.

Desc.CHS: 指针的旋转不会有尽头，但少女受人宠爱的岁月则相反。
Desc.EN: The hands of time will never come to an end, but the same cannot not be said for those cherished years of the young maiden's life when she was doted upon.

Desc.CHS: 属于红茶而不属于烈酒，属于芳甜而不属于苦涩的杯皿。
Desc.EN: A vessel made with sweet black tea in mind rather than bitter liquor.

Desc.CHS: 永远娇嫩的鲜花，历经长久时光仍不枯萎地散发着芬芳。
Desc.EN: A fragrant flower that will bloom for all eternity and never wither.

Desc.CHS: 指针的旋转不会有尽头，但少女受人宠爱的岁月则相反。
Desc.EN: The hands of time will never come to an end, but the same cannot not be said for those cherished years of the young maiden's life when she was doted upon.

Desc.CHS: 传说中是能耐流火高热的杯盏，如今其中空无一物仅有余温。
Desc.EN: A legendary goblet that can withstand extremely high temperatures. It still retains a degree of warmth even though it is now empty.

Desc.CHS: 浴火的孤高之鸟的羽毛，似乎能从中听到野火里的振翅之声。
Desc.EN: The feather of a proud phoenix. You can almost hear the sound of its wings flapping in the scorching flames.

Desc.CHS: 渡过火海的智者之冠，曾经映照着在热浪中挺立的古老身影。
Desc.EN: The circlet of a sage who traversed a sea of fire. It once shone brightly from their ancient silhouette as they stood strong amidst the flames.

Desc.CHS: 在烈焰的簇拥下盛开的花朵，传说古代智者佩着它走进了火海。
Desc.EN: A flower that blooms amidst burning flames. It is said that long ago, a sage once wore it as he walked into a sea of fire.

Desc.CHS: 流淌着闪烁热砂的沙漏。流沙匆匆而去，从不留下任何烙印。
Desc.EN: Burning sand flows within this hourglass. Despite the intense heat, the sand leave no mark upon the vessel that houses it.

Desc.CHS: 传说中是能耐流火高热的杯盏，如今其中空无一物仅有余温。
Desc.EN: A legendary goblet that can withstand extremely high temperatures. It still retains a degree of warmth even though it is now empty.

Desc.EN: The circlet of a sage who traversed a sea of fire. It once shone brightly from their ancient silhouette as they stood strong amidst the flames.

Desc.CHS: 在烈焰的簇拥下盛开的花朵，传说古代智者佩着它走进了火海。
Desc.EN: A flower that blooms amidst burning flames. It is said that long ago, a sage once wore it as he walked into a sea of fire.

Desc.CHS: 流淌着闪烁热砂的沙漏。流沙匆匆而去，从不留下任何烙印。
Desc.EN: Burning sand flows within this hourglass. Despite the intense heat, the sand leave no mark upon the vessel that houses it.

Desc.CHS: 平雷勇士的酒盏，据说平息了雷之魔兽的英雄曾用这尊酒盏满盛紫电为饮。
Desc.EN: The wine goblet from which the Thundersoother, who defeated the Beast of Thunder, once drank violet lightning.

Desc.CHS: 在传说中，挺身平息了雷电的勇武英雄的徽章，是翱翔于狂雷的猛禽之羽。
Desc.EN: The feather of a predatory bird that soars through lightning storms. It was said to have been adopted as an insignia by the legendary hero who pacified thunder and lightning.

Desc.CHS: 平雷勇士的冠冕，是古老的英雄击败了危害大地的雷之魔兽而获得的华冠。
Desc.EN: The crown given to the Thundersoother for defeating the Beast of Thunder that had been wreaking havoc upon the land.

Desc.CHS: 仅于雷霆之怒中傲然盛放的花朵，至今仍能赐予行走在雷雨中的游人勇气。
Desc.EN: A flower that blooms even amidst ferocious thunder and lightning. To this day, it still grants courage to travelers in thunderstorms.

Desc.CHS: 镇服雷电的勇士持有的时计，其中的雷之碎晶随流逝如雷如电的时间泻落。
Desc.EN: A timepiece kept by the hero who conquered thunder and lightning. The tiny shards of Electro crystal within flow back and forth with the passing of time.

Desc.CHS: 平雷勇士的酒盏，据说平息了雷之魔兽的英雄曾用这尊酒盏满盛紫电为饮。
Desc.EN: The wine goblet from which the Thundersoother, who defeated the Beast of Thunder, once drank violet lightning.

Desc.CHS: 在传说中，挺身平息了雷电的勇武英雄的徽章，是翱翔于狂雷的猛禽之羽。
Desc.EN: The feather of a predatory bird that soars through lightning storms. It was said to have been adopted as an insignia by the legendary hero who pacified thunder and lightning.

Desc.EN: The crown given to the Thundersoother for defeating the Beast of Thunder that had been wreaking havoc upon the land.

Desc.CHS: 仅于雷霆之怒中傲然盛放的花朵，至今仍能赐予行走在雷雨中的游人勇气。
Desc.EN: A flower that blooms even amidst ferocious thunder and lightning. To this day, it still grants courage to travelers in thunderstorms.

Desc.CHS: 镇服雷电的勇士持有的时计，其中的雷之碎晶随流逝如雷如电的时间泻落。
Desc.EN: A timepiece kept by the hero who conquered thunder and lightning. The tiny shards of Electro crystal within flow back and forth with the passing of time.

Desc.CHS: 用寒冰雕制成的杯盏，如冬天一般坚利。曾经的主人从中啜饮过不冻之酒。
Desc.EN: A cup carved out of ice that is as chilly and biting as winter. Its former master would drink an unfreezable liquor from it.

Desc.CHS: 散布寒冬的鸟羽，仿佛能感受到猛禽在雪原与冰峰之上呼号翱翔的振翅之风。
Desc.EN: A feather that exudes a chilly aura. One can almost feel the turbulent winds that brought it here, wailing over snow-covered plains and between frosty peaks.

Desc.CHS: 梦想征服冰雪的古代英雄冠冕，是驱使它的故主直面刻骨寒冬的勇气之证。
Desc.EN: The crown of an ancient hero who dreamt of conquering the cold. It is proof of its former master's bravery in facing the bone-chilling cold of winter.

Desc.CHS: 早已绝迹的冰川之花，霜结着点点冰露。孤高的勇士也曾为这朵鲜花折腰。
Desc.EN: A long-extinct flower, covered in beads of frost, that once grew on the glaciers. There was a time when even the proudest and most arrogant warriors bowed before it.

Desc.CHS: 等待勇士归来的故国人民所用的时计。其中流淌的并不是沙，而是不化的冰屑。
Desc.EN: A timepiece from a nation of old that waited for their warriors' return. What flows inside is not sand, but bits of ice that never melt.

Desc.CHS: 用寒冰雕制成的杯盏，如冬天一般坚利。曾经的主人从中啜饮过不冻之酒。
Desc.EN: A cup carved out of ice that is as chilly and biting as winter. Its former master would drink an unfreezable liquor from it.

Desc.EN: A feather that exudes a chilly aura. One can almost feel the turbulent winds that brought it here, wailing over snow-covered plains and between frosty peaks.

Desc.EN: The crown of an ancient hero who dreamt of conquering the cold. It is proof of its former master's bravery in facing the bone-chilling cold of winter.

Desc.EN: A timepiece from a nation of old that waited for their warriors' return. What flows inside is not sand, but bits of ice that never melt.

Desc.CHS: 属于红茶而不属于烈酒，属于芳甜而不属于苦涩的杯皿。
Desc.EN: A vessel made with sweet black tea in mind rather than bitter liquor.

Desc.CHS: 寄托谁人的思念的羽饰，就如与风一同去往远方的候鸟。
Desc.EN: A feathered accessory that carries the longing for a certain someone, like a migratory bird on the wind.

Desc.CHS: 精心保养的女士帽，即使是眼角的皱纹也可以完美遮盖。
Desc.EN: A meticulously well-maintained woman's hat that keeps wrinkles safely out of sight.

Desc.EN: The hands of time will never come to an end, but the same cannot not be said for those cherished years of the young maiden's life when she was doted upon.

Desc.CHS: 金属的容器。可以用来装某种能排遣漫长守望带来的孤独的液体。
Desc.EN: A metal vessel that can be filled with a drink to dispel the loneliness of the long watch.

Desc.CHS: 象征着某人「渴望成为坚盾」的羽形别针。
Desc.EN: A feather-shaped brooch that symbolizes someone’s yearning to defend others like a shield.

Desc.CHS: 被夜色染得靛青的织物。能在紧急时充当绷带。
Desc.EN: A fabric band dyed indigo by the darkness of night. Can also double as a bandage in the event of an emergency.

Desc.CHS: 守护者珍视的鸢尾花。并没有机会送给倾心的人。
Desc.EN: An iris that was cherished by the guardian. Unfortunately, the chance never came for it to be given to whom the guardian loved.

Desc.CHS: 展示当前时间的小道具，在没有月亮的黑夜里是唯一的时间参照。
Desc.EN: A small timekeeping gadget. On moonless nights, it was the only way its former owner could know the time.

Desc.CHS: 金属的容器。可以用来装某种能排遣漫长守望带来的孤独的液体。
Desc.EN: A metal vessel that can be filled with a drink to dispel the loneliness of the long watch.

Desc.CHS: 展示当前时间的小道具，在没有月亮的黑夜里是唯一的时间参照。
Desc.EN: A small timekeeping gadget. On moonless nights, it was the only way its former owner could know the time.

Desc.CHS: 华丽而不失庄重的酒樽，千年前曾满盛玉露。
Desc.EN: A resplendent yet dignified wine goblet, once filled to the brim in an era long gone.

Desc.CHS: 来自矶岩巨鸢的刚羽，玄石的羽尖有时会凝结有清冷的露珠。
Desc.EN: A hard feather from a large seacliff hawk. The basalt tip of the feather sometimes glistens with a cool dew.

Desc.CHS: 玄岩精雕而成的庄严面具，空洞的双眼永远冰冷地凝视着前方。
Desc.EN: A solemn mask exquisitely carved from basalt. Its hollow eyes stare ahead expressionless and cold.

Desc.CHS: 盛开于磐陀巨岩的金石之花。花瓣随风轻摇，似有生机。
Desc.EN: A flower born of the minerals and rocks of cliffside cracks. The way its petals blow in the wind makes it seem alive.

Desc.CHS: 以整块圭璧雕琢而成的日晷，纹路层叠星罗，沉默地记录着失去的时间。
Desc.EN: A sundial carved from a single, large piece of jade. Its lined with a pattern that silently records the passage of time.

Desc.EN: A resplendent yet dignified wine goblet, once filled to the brim in an era long gone.

Desc.CHS: 以整块圭璧雕琢而成的日晷，纹路层叠星罗，沉默地记录着失去的时间。
Desc.EN: A sundial carved from a single, large piece of jade. Its lined with a pattern that silently records the passage of time.

Desc.CHS: 夏祭时，盛水气球并不罕见。但如此精致的仅此一个。
Desc.EN: Water balloons can be seen everywhere during the summer festival, but none are as finely-wrought as this one.

Desc.CHS: 精致的木造飞镖。抵达终点时才会停滞之物。
Desc.EN: A well-crafted wooden dart. It will only stop once it has reached its destination.

Desc.CHS: 依据传说中的神明形象制作的，十分流行的面具。
Desc.EN: A popular mask cast in the image of a deity, as described in the legends.

Desc.CHS: 永远盛放的人造之花，其中是否具有生命呢。
Desc.EN: A man-made flower in eternal bloom. Who knows if there truly is life in there?

Desc.CHS: 停滞在某一时刻的精致怀钟。
Desc.EN: A pocketwatch that has stopped at a certain point in time.

Desc.CHS: 夏祭时，盛水气球并不罕见。但如此精致的仅此一个。
Desc.EN: Water balloons can be seen everywhere during the summer festival, but none are as finely-wrought as this one.

Desc.EN: A popular mask cast in the image of a deity, as described in the legends.

Desc.EN: A man-made flower in eternal bloom. Who knows if there truly is life in there?

Desc.CHS: 停滞在某一时刻的精致怀钟。
Desc.EN: A pocketwatch that has stopped at a certain point in time.

Desc.CHS: 虽然在外人看来只是普通的茶杯，但在学员眼里可是教官权力的象征。
Desc.EN: It may seem like an ordinary tea cup to most. But to students, it is the symbol of the instructor's authority.

Desc.CHS: 熟知如何化解攻击力道的教官，不会让这种羽饰被劲风吹掉。
Desc.EN: Any instructor who has mastered the art of de-escalation knows to keep this accessory firmly in their grasp at all times.

Desc.CHS: 制式的教官帽子。是拒绝了晋升的军官才能获得的殊荣。
Desc.EN: A standard-issue honorary instructor's cap, only granted to those who turn down a promotion.

Desc.CHS: 教官的胸口别着这种花的时候，意味着今日不练兵。
Desc.EN: Whenever the instructor wore this brooch, it meant there would be no training sessions that day.

Desc.CHS: 不能用来看时间的怀表，是完全奉献给训练的计时工具。
Desc.EN: A stopwatch used not for general timekeeping but to measure the duration of a training session.

Desc.CHS: 虽然在外人看来只是普通的茶杯，但在学员眼里可是教官权力的象征。

Desc.EN: A standard-issue honorary instructor's cap, only granted to those who turn down a promotion.

Desc.CHS: 教官的胸口别着这种花的时候，意味着今日不练兵。
Desc.EN: Whenever the instructor wore this brooch, it meant there would be no training sessions that day.

Desc.CHS: 不能用来看时间的怀表，是完全奉献给训练的计时工具。
Desc.EN: A stopwatch used not for general timekeeping but to measure the duration of a training session.

Desc.CHS: 用不知名的巨大兽类的骨头制成的杯。是某次厮杀后得到的猎获。
Desc.EN: A goblet made from the bone of an unknown beast. It was taken as a trophy after some deadly encounter.

Desc.CHS: 原本传说中报丧之鸟的黯蓝尾羽，一部分被染成了红色。
Desc.EN: An indigo feather from a legendary raven, part of which has been dyed crimson red.

Desc.CHS: 在不顾生死的厮杀中一半破碎的骇人铁面具。
Desc.EN: A hideous iron mask that has been left half-shattered from vicious battles.

Desc.CHS: 被染红的精致花朵，与狂战士的气质微妙地相符。
Desc.EN: An exquisite flower that has been dyed red. It represents the qualities of the Berserker.

Desc.CHS: 永远无情流动着的器物。提醒着狂战士自己在战场上的时限，和在人世间的时限。
Desc.EN: An instrument with an eternal flow that continues mercilessly within, reminding the Berserker of the limited time he has left — both on the battlefield as well as in the world.

Desc.CHS: 永远无情流动着的器物。提醒着狂战士自己在战场上的时限，和在人世间的时限。
Desc.EN: An instrument with an eternal flow that continues mercilessly within, reminding the Berserker of the limited time he has left — both on the battlefield as well as in the world.

Desc.CHS: 无心打捞上来的褪色酒盏，暗淡的外观呢喃着海波之底的往日。
Desc.EN: A faded wine cup that was unintentionally dredged up from the sea. Its dull exterior tells of the days it has spent beneath the waves.

Desc.CHS: 随呜咽的海风、腥红的海浪而来的飞羽，年岁改变了它的形状与颜色。
Desc.EN: A feather carried over by whimpering sea winds and crimson waves. The passage of time has changed its shape and color.

Desc.CHS: 古旧的船帽，缭绕着不散的酒气、浸渍了斑驳的酒痕。
Desc.EN: An ancient, wine-stained sea hat that still reeks of alcohol even now.

Desc.CHS: 色泽暗淡的斗篷别针。原本镀上的金色已经被海风磨去。
Desc.EN: A mantle brooch that has lost its luster. The gold plating that once adorned it was ground away by the wind and the waves long ago.

Desc.CHS: 古旧的铜制罗盘，指针始终朝向遥不可及的彼岸，不存在的港湾。
Desc.EN: An ancient bronze compass. Its needle points towards some ever-distant shore, to a non-existent harbor.

Desc.EN: A faded wine cup that was unintentionally dredged up from the sea. Its dull exterior tells of the days it has spent beneath the waves.

Desc.EN: An ancient bronze compass. Its needle points towards some ever-distant shore, to a non-existent harbor.

Desc.CHS: 千岩军用以盟誓的金爵，依旧残留着丝丝酒香。
Desc.EN: A golden cup used by the Millelith to take their oaths. Still bears the lovely scent of wine.

Desc.CHS: 在仪仗场合佩戴的鹰翎，用以向外人显明璃月港的威严与决心。
Desc.EN: A falcon feather worn on ceremonial occasions. It displays the dignity and resolve of Liyue Harbor to the outside world.

Desc.CHS: 年代久远的华丽头盔，洗净尘沙后依旧明亮如新。
Desc.EN: A splendorous helmet from ages past. Clean the dust away and it will look brand-new once more.

Desc.CHS: 以金箔制成的精致花朵，象征了其主人所获得的功勋与荣誉。
Desc.EN: A flower made from gold leaf. It represents the glories and honors attained by its wearer.

Desc.CHS: 外观朴素的计时道具，在战乱的时代，一度是千岩军的制式装备。
Desc.EN: A simple device for telling time. This was once standard-issue for the Millelith during times of war.

Desc.CHS: 千岩军用以盟誓的金爵，依旧残留着丝丝酒香。
Desc.EN: A golden cup used by the Millelith to take their oaths. Still bears the lovely scent of wine.

Desc.EN: A splendorous helmet from ages past. Clean the dust away and it will look brand-new once more.

Desc.CHS: 以金箔制成的精致花朵，象征了其主人所获得的功勋与荣誉。
Desc.EN: A flower made from gold leaf. It represents the glories and honors attained by its wearer.

Desc.CHS: 外观朴素的计时道具，在战乱的时代，一度是千岩军的制式装备。
Desc.EN: A simple device for telling time. This was once standard-issue for the Millelith during times of war.

Desc.CHS: 从外观无从断定经历了多少岁月的精致杯盏。
Desc.EN: An intricately-made cup. Its appearance betrays nothing of its age to an observer.

Desc.CHS: 边缘无比锐利的不祥翎羽，或许象征着异类的不羁。
Desc.EN: An ominous pinion with edges of unsurpassed keenness. Perhaps it represents an unnaturally uninhibited nature.

Desc.CHS: 能将面目遮蔽，让人无从判断表情的面具。
Desc.EN: A mask that covers the face, hiding one's expression from others.

Desc.CHS: 湛蓝而坚硬，永不凋败、永不褪色的人造花朵。
Desc.EN: A hard, blue artificial flower. Its petals shall never wither, nor shall its colors fade.

Desc.CHS: 壳罩无法打开的怀表，会坚定地随着时光流逝而嘀嗒作响。
Desc.EN: A pocket watch with a cover that cannot be opened. Yet it ticks and tocks away, following the inexorable flow of time.

Desc.CHS: 从外观无从断定经历了多少岁月的精致杯盏。

Desc.EN: A mask that covers the face, hiding one's expression from others.

Desc.CHS: 湛蓝而坚硬，永不凋败、永不褪色的人造花朵。
Desc.EN: A hard, blue artificial flower. Its petals shall never wither, nor shall its colors fade.

Desc.CHS: 壳罩无法打开的怀表，会坚定地随着时光流逝而嘀嗒作响。
Desc.EN: A pocket watch with a cover that cannot be opened. Yet it ticks and tocks away, following the inexorable flow of time.

Desc.CHS: 特制的占卜签筒，底部的机关能让人轻易抽掉不想要的愿签。
Desc.EN: A special fortune-telling cylindrical object. The mechanism at the bottom allows one to easily remove all unwanted wish sticks.

Desc.CHS: 样式有点古旧的破魔矢，似乎一直被某人精心保存着。
Desc.EN: A demon-slaying arrow of a rather ancient make. It seems to have been preserved with great care by someone, even until the present day.

Desc.CHS: 保存良好的祭礼狐面，永远带着一副神秘的浅笑。
Desc.EN: A well-preserved ceremonial fox mask. A small, enigmatic smile ever graces its lips.

Desc.CHS: 精美的水引御守，据说能够封存实现愿望的力量。
Desc.EN: A lovely amulet made from twisted paper cord. It is said to hold the power to make wishes come true.

Desc.CHS: 以水引和铃铛装饰的青铜怀表，时间永远停在了某个秋日的黎明。
Desc.EN: A bronze pocket watch adorned with twisted paper cord and a bell. Its hands are forever frozen at the dawn of a certain autumn day.

Desc.CHS: 特制的占卜签筒，底部的机关能让人轻易抽掉不想要的愿签。
Desc.EN: A special fortune-telling cylindrical object. The mechanism at the bottom allows one to easily remove all unwanted wish sticks.

Desc.EN: A demon-slaying arrow of a rather ancient make. It seems to have been preserved with great care by someone, even until the present day.

Desc.CHS: 保存良好的祭礼狐面，永远带着一副神秘的浅笑。
Desc.EN: A well-preserved ceremonial fox mask. A small, enigmatic smile ever graces its lips.

Desc.CHS: 精美的水引御守，据说能够封存实现愿望的力量。
Desc.EN: A lovely amulet made from twisted paper cord. It is said to hold the power to make wishes come true.

Desc.CHS: 以水引和铃铛装饰的青铜怀表，时间永远停在了某个秋日的黎明。
Desc.EN: A bronze pocket watch adorned with twisted paper cord and a bell. Its hands are forever frozen at the dawn of a certain autumn day.

Desc.CHS: 精致的酒壶，曾经是名震天下的武人载酒的容器。
Desc.EN: An intricately-designed wine vessel that a world-famous martial artist once drank from.

Desc.CHS: 原本属于某名天狗的黑羽，是过去的剑豪珍惜的纪念品。
Desc.EN: This was once the black feather of a certain tengu warrior, and was the treasured souvenir of an ancient swordsman.

Desc.CHS: 坚实牢固的兜盔，是身份尊贵的武人的护身之物。
Desc.EN: A sturdy and hard helmet worn as armor by a noble samurai.

Desc.CHS: 传说中背叛了将军的鬼人，曾经获赐的刀上的华美宝镡。
Desc.EN: Legends hold that this ornate hand guard was once fitted upon a sword gifted to the oni who betrayed the Shogun.

Desc.CHS: 黑地堇漆的考究印笼，其上装饰着发亮的螺钿与精致的金具。
Desc.EN: An exquisite seal cage patterned with pansies painted upon a black backdrop, decorated with shining inlaid seashells and intricate gold-work.

Desc.CHS: 精致的酒壶，曾经是名震天下的武人载酒的容器。
Desc.EN: An intricately-designed wine vessel that a world-famous martial artist once drank from.

Desc.EN: This was once the black feather of a certain tengu warrior, and was the treasured souvenir of an ancient swordsman.

Desc.EN: A sturdy and hard helmet worn as armor by a noble samurai.

Desc.EN: Legends hold that this ornate hand guard was once fitted upon a sword gifted to the oni who betrayed the Shogun.

Desc.CHS: 黑地堇漆的考究印笼，其上装饰着发亮的螺钿与精致的金具。
Desc.EN: An exquisite seal cage patterned with pansies painted upon a black backdrop, decorated with shining inlaid seashells and intricate gold-work.

Desc.CHS: 以黑漆与金粉装饰过的葫芦，已看不出本来的颜色，好像主要作用是演出的道具。
Desc.EN: A gourd that has been adorned with powdered gold and black paint. Its original color can no longer be discerned, but its main use seems to be as a performance prop.

Desc.CHS: 于避世之幽馆中一同带出的箭羽状的凭证，因创造者的怜悯之情，而与某具沉睡之躯一同置于馆中。
Desc.EN: A feather-shaped token that was brought forth from a secluded hall. The compassion of its creator led to it being left within that mansion along with a certain slumbering form.

Desc.CHS: 流浪者在旅途中遮光避雨的斗笠，但后来却成为了遮挡面目、隐藏表情的便利道具。
Desc.EN: A hat that once shielded a wanderer from sun and rain. It eventually became a convenient tool with which faces might be hidden and expressions obscured.

Desc.CHS: 六瓣花形状的小型金饰，以永不凋零之姿，阅遍俗世易逝的荣华。
Desc.EN: A small golden ornament with six petals that shall never wilt. It symbolizes the transience of mortal glories.

Desc.CHS: 于稻妻而言乃是舶来品的小物件。名为机芯的零件已被卸下，指针也不再转动。
Desc.EN: As far as Inazuma is concerned, this is some small object from overseas. The heart of this mechanism has been removed, and its hands no longer turn.

Desc.CHS: 以黑漆与金粉装饰过的葫芦，已看不出本来的颜色，好像主要作用是演出的道具。

Desc.EN: As far as Inazuma is concerned, this is some small object from overseas. The heart of this mechanism has been removed, and its hands no longer turn.

Desc.CHS: 海祇岛的巫女们所供奉的明珠，始终闪烁着点点光芒，从未黯淡。
Desc.EN: The shining pearls that the shrine maidens of Watatsumi Island offer up shine eternally and never dim.

Desc.CHS: 与珊瑚同色的柔弱彩羽，据说出自巫女的羽衣。
Desc.EN: A down feather with the same hue as coral, said to come from a shrine maiden's ceremonial garment.

Desc.CHS: 古老精致的冠冕，由被遗忘的「神人」所拥有。如今被海祇之民精心封存起来。
Desc.EN: An ancient, intricate crown that was once used by a forgotten clergy member. Today, this relic has been enshrined with great ceremony by the people of Watatsumi.

Desc.CHS: 染上多变海色的轻柔之花，在月光下闪烁着奇妙的色彩。
Desc.EN: A soft flower that has taken on the many shades of the capricious ocean. It shines with wondrous colors under the moon's silver light.

Desc.CHS: 明净无垢的贝壳，来自深邃无底的大海。
Desc.EN: A clean, flawless seashell that comes from the bottomless ocean.

Desc.CHS: 早已绝迹的冰川之花，霜结着点点冰露。孤高的勇士也曾为这朵鲜花折腰。
Desc.EN: A long-extinct flower, covered in beads of frost, that once grew on the glaciers. There was a time when even the proudest and most arrogant warriors bowed before it.

Desc.EN: A feather that exudes a chilly aura. One can almost feel the turbulent winds that brought it here, wailing over snow-covered plains and between frosty peaks.

Desc.EN: The golden cup a champion gladiator drank from in ancient times. It brimmed with his glory for years until the fateful day of his fall.

Desc.CHS: 盛开于磐陀巨岩的金石之花。花瓣随风轻摇，似有生机。

Desc.CHS: 生命值低于70%时，暴击率额外提升24%。
Desc.EN: When HP is below 70%, CRIT Rate increases by an additional 24%.

Desc.CHS: 普通攻击与重击造成的伤害提高15%；
Desc.EN: Increases Normal Attack and Charged Attack DMG by 15%.

Desc.CHS: 施放元素战技后的8秒内，普通攻击和重击造成的伤害提升25%。
Desc.EN: After using Elemental Skill, increases Normal Attack and Charged Attack DMG by 25% for 8s.

Desc.CHS: 元素精通提高80点。
Desc.EN: Increases Elemental Mastery by 80.

Desc.CHS: 触发元素反应后，队伍中所有角色的元素精通提高120点，持续8秒。
Desc.EN: Upon triggering an Elemental Reaction, increases all party members' Elemental Mastery by 120 for 8s.

Desc.CHS: 元素战技造成的伤害提升20%。
Desc.EN: Increases Elemental Skill DMG by 20%.

Desc.CHS: 击败敌人时，有100%概率清除元素战技的冷却时间。该效果每15秒至多触发一次。
Desc.EN: Defeating an opponent has a 100% chance to remove Elemental Skill CD. Can only occur once every 15s.

Desc.CHS: 元素充能效率提高20%。
Desc.EN: Energy Recharge +20%

Desc.CHS: 施放元素爆发后，每2秒为队伍中所有角色（不包括自己）恢复2点元素能量。该效果持续6秒，无法叠加。
Desc.EN: Using an Elemental Burst regenerates 2 Energy for all party members (excluding the wearer) every 2s for 6s. This effect cannot stack.

Desc.CHS: 生命值上限提高1000点。
Desc.EN: Max HP increased by 1000.

Desc.CHS: 开启各类宝箱后的5秒内，持续恢复30%生命值。
Desc.EN: Opening a chest regenerates 30% Max HP over 5s.

Desc.CHS: 防御力提高100点。
Desc.EN: DEF increased by 100.

Desc.CHS: 拾取摩拉时，恢复300点生命值。
Desc.EN: Picking up Mora restores 300 HP.

Desc.CHS: 元素充能效率提高20%。
Desc.EN: Energy Recharge +20%

Desc.CHS: 获得元素微粒或元素晶球时，队伍中所有弓箭和法器角色额外恢复3点元素能量。该效果每3秒只能触发一次。
Desc.EN: Gaining Elemental Particles or Orbs gives 3 Energy to all party members who have a bow or a catalyst equipped. Can only occur once every 3s.

Desc.CHS: 角色受到的治疗效果提高20%。
Desc.EN: Increases incoming healing by 20%.

Desc.CHS: 施放元素爆发时，恢复20%生命值。
Desc.EN: Using Elemental Burst restores 20% HP.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%冰元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Cryo DMG Bonus +15%

Desc.CHS: 攻击处于冰元素影响下的敌人时，暴击率提高20%；若敌人处于冻结状态下，则暴击率额外提高20%。
Desc.EN: When a character attacks an opponent affected by Cryo, their CRIT Rate is increased by 20%. If the opponent is Frozen, CRIT Rate is increased by an additional 20%.

Desc.CHS: 雷元素抗性提高40%。
Desc.EN: Electro RES increased by 40%.

Desc.CHS: 对处于雷元素影响下的敌人造成的伤害提升35%。
Desc.EN: Increases DMG against opponents affected by Electro by 35%.

Desc.CHS: 火元素抗性提高40%。
Desc.EN: Pyro RES increased by 40%.

Desc.CHS: 对处于火元素影响下的敌人造成的伤害提升35%。
Desc.EN: Increases DMG against opponents affected by Pyro by 35%.

Desc.CHS: 角色造成的治疗效果提升15%。
Desc.EN: Character Healing Effectiveness +15%

Desc.CHS: 施放元素战技或元素爆发后的10秒内，队伍中所有角色受治疗效果加成提高20%。
Desc.EN: Using an Elemental Skill or Burst increases healing received by all party members by 20% for 10s.

Desc.CHS: 攻击力提高18%。
装备该圣遗物套装的角色为单手剑、双手剑、长柄武器角色时，角色普通攻击造成的伤害提高35%。
Desc.EN: If the wielder of this artifact set uses a Sword, Claymore or Polearm, increases their Normal Attack DMG by 35%.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%风元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Anemo DMG Bonus +15%

Desc.CHS: 扩散反应造成的伤害提升60%。根据扩散的元素类型，降低受到影响的敌人40%的对应元素抗性，持续10秒。
Desc.EN: Increases Swirl DMG by 60%. Decreases opponent's Elemental RES to the element infused in the Swirl by 40% for 10s.

Desc.CHS: 元素精通提高80点。
Desc.EN: Increases Elemental Mastery by 80.

Desc.CHS: 装备该圣遗物套装的角色为法器、弓箭角色时，角色重击造成的伤害提高35%。
Desc.EN: Increases Charged Attack DMG by 35% if the character uses a Catalyst or a Bow.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%冰元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Cryo DMG Bonus +15%

Desc.CHS: 超导反应造成的伤害提升100%，融化反应的加成系数提高15%。施放元素爆发后的10秒内，冰元素伤害加成额外提升30%。
Desc.EN: Increases Superconduct DMG by 100%. Increases Melt DMG by 15%. Using an Elemental Burst increases Cryo DMG Bonus by 30% for 10s.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%雷元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Electro DMG Bonus +15%

Desc.CHS: 超载、感电、超导反应造成的伤害提升40%。触发这些元素反应时，元素战技冷却时间减少1秒。该效果每0.8秒最多触发一次。
Desc.EN: Increases damage caused by Overloaded, Electro-Charged and Superconduct by 40%. Triggering such effects decreases Elemental Skill CD by 1s. Can only occur once every 0.8s.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%火元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Pyro DMG Bonus +15%

Desc.CHS: 超载、燃烧反应造成的伤害提升40%，蒸发、融化反应的加成系数提高15%。施放元素战技后的10秒内，2件套的效果提高50%，该效果最多叠加3次。
Desc.EN: Increases Overloaded and Burning DMG by 40%. Increases Vaporize and Melt DMG by 15%. Using Elemental Skill increases the 2-Piece Set Bonus by 50% of its starting value for 10s. Max 3 stacks.

Desc.CHS: 元素爆发造成的伤害提升20%。
Desc.EN: Elemental Burst DMG +20%

Desc.CHS: 施放元素爆发后，队伍中所有角色攻击力提升20%，持续12秒。该效果不可叠加。
Desc.EN: Using an Elemental Burst increases all party members' ATK by 20% for 12s. This effect cannot stack.

Desc.CHS: 造成的物理伤害提高25%。
Desc.EN: Physical DMG +25%

Desc.CHS: 击败敌人后的10秒内，施放重击时不消耗体力，且重击造成的伤害提升50%。
Desc.EN: After defeating an opponent, increases Charged Attack DMG by 50%, and reduces its Stamina cost to 0 for 10s.

Desc.CHS: 受到的火元素附着效果的持续时间减少40%。
Desc.EN: Affected by Pyro for 40% less time.

Desc.CHS: 受到的水元素附着效果的持续时间减少40%。
Desc.EN: Affected by Hydro for 40% less time.

Desc.CHS: 受到的雷元素附着效果的持续时间减少40%。
Desc.EN: Affected by Electro for 40% less time.

Desc.CHS: 受到的风元素附着效果的持续时间减少40%。
Desc.EN: Affected by Anemo for 40% less time.

Desc.CHS: 受到的冰元素附着效果的持续时间减少40%。
Desc.EN: Affected by Cryo for 40% less time.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%岩元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Gain a 15% Geo DMG Bonus.

Desc.CHS: 获得结晶反应形成的晶片时，队伍中所有角色获得35%对应元素伤害加成，持续10秒。同时只能通过该效果获得一种元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Upon obtaining an Elemental Shard created through a Crystallize Reaction, all party members gain a 35% DMG Bonus for that particular element for 10s. Only one form of Elemental DMG Bonus can be gained in this manner at any one time.

Desc.CHS: 护盾强效提高35%。
Desc.EN: Increases Shield Strength by 35%.

Desc.CHS: 处于护盾庇护下时，额外获得40%普通攻击和重击伤害加成。
Desc.EN: While protected by a shield, gain an additional 40% Normal and Charged Attack DMG.

Desc.CHS: 获得15%水元素伤害加成。
Desc.EN: Hydro DMG Bonus +15%

Desc.CHS: 施放元素战技后的15秒内，普通攻击与重击造成的伤害提高30%。
Desc.EN: After using Elemental Skill, increases Normal Attack and Charged Attack DMG by 30% for 15s.

Desc.CHS: 生命值提升20%
Desc.EN: HP increased by 20%.

Desc.CHS: 元素战技命中敌人后，使队伍中附近的所有角色攻击力提升20%，护盾强效提升30%，持续3秒。该效果每0.5秒至多触发一次。装备此圣遗物套装的角色处于队伍后台时，依然能触发该效果。
Desc.EN: When an Elemental Skill hits an opponent, the ATK of all nearby party members is increased by 20% and their Shield Strength is increased by 30% for 3s. This effect can be triggered once every 0.5s. This effect can still be triggered even when the character who is using this artifact set is not on the field.

Desc.CHS: 造成的物理伤害提高25%。
Desc.EN: Physical DMG is increased by 25%.

Desc.CHS: 元素战技命中敌人后，攻击力提升9%。该效果持续7秒，至多叠加2层，每0.3秒至多触发一次。叠满2层时，2件套的效果提升100%。
Desc.EN: When an Elemental Skill hits an opponent, ATK is increased by 9% for 7s. This effect stacks up to 2 times and can be triggered once every 0.3s. Once 2 stacks are reached, the 2-set effect is increased by 100%.

Desc.CHS: 攻击力提高18%。
施放元素战技时，如果角色的元素能量高于或等于15点，则会流失15点元素能量，使接下来的10秒内，普通攻击、重击、下落攻击造成的伤害提高50%，持续期间内该效果不会再次触发。
Desc.EN: When casting an Elemental Skill, if the character has 15 or more Energy, they lose 15 Energy and Normal/Charged/Plunging Attack DMG is increased by 50% for 10s. This effect will not trigger again during that duration.

Desc.CHS: 元素充能效率提高20%。
Desc.EN: Energy Recharge +20%

Desc.CHS: 基于元素充能效率的25%，提高元素爆发造成的伤害。至多通过这种方式获得75%提升。
Desc.EN: Increases Elemental Burst DMG by 25% of Energy Recharge. A maximum of 75% bonus DMG can be obtained in this way.

Desc.CHS: 防御力提高30%。
Desc.EN: DEF +30%

Desc.CHS: 装备此圣遗物套装的角色在以下情况下，将获得「问答」效果：在场上用岩元素攻击命中敌人后获得一层，每0.3秒至多触发一次；在队伍后台中，每3秒获得一层。问答至多叠加4层，每层能提供6%防御力与6%岩元素伤害加成。每6秒，若未获得问答效果，将损失一层。
Desc.EN: A character equipped with this Artifact set will obtain the Curiosity effect in the following conditions: When on the field, the character gains 1 stack after hitting an opponent with a Geo attack, triggering a maximum of once every 0.3s. When off the field, the character gains 1 stack every 3s. Curiosity can stack up to 4 times, each providing 6% DEF and a 6% Geo DMG Bonus. When 6 seconds pass without gaining a Curiosity stack, 1 stack is lost.

Desc.CHS: 治疗加成提高15%。
Desc.EN: Healing Bonus +15%.

Desc.CHS: 装备此圣遗物套装的角色对队伍中的角色进行治疗时，将产生持续3秒的海染泡沫，记录治疗的生命值回复量（包括溢出值）。持续时间结束时，海染泡沫将会爆炸，对周围的敌人造成90%累计回复量的伤害（该伤害结算方式同感电、超导等元素反应，但不受元素精通、等级或反应伤害加成效果影响）。每3.5秒至多产生一个海染泡沫；海染泡沫至多记录30000点回复量，含溢出部分的治疗量；自己的队伍中同时至多存在一个海染泡沫。装备此圣遗物套装的角色处于队伍后台时，依然能触发该效果。
Desc.EN: When the character equipping this artifact set heals a character in the party, a Sea-Dyed Foam will appear for 3 seconds, accumulating the amount of HP recovered from healing (including overflow healing). At the end of the duration, the Sea-Dyed Foam will explode, dealing DMG to nearby opponents based on 90% of the accumulated healing. (This DMG is calculated similarly to Reactions such as Electro-Charged, and Superconduct, but is not affected by Elemental Mastery, Character Levels, or Reaction DMG Bonuses). Only one Sea-Dyed Foam can be produced every 3.5 seconds. Each Sea-Dyed Foam can accumulate up to 30,000 HP (including overflow healing). There can be no more than one Sea-Dyed Foam active at any given time. This effect can still be triggered even when the character who is using this artifact set is not on the field.
